<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>X509 on ErrorCode — Error Code Reference &amp; Solutions</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tags/x509/</link><description>Recent content in X509 on ErrorCode — Error Code Reference &amp; Solutions</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>en</language><atom:link href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tags/x509/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>[Solution] C Certificate has expired</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/c/certificate-expired/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/c/certificate-expired/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="certificate-has-expired"&gt;Certificate has expired&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;An expired certificate means the X.509 certificate&amp;rsquo;s validity period has passed. SSL/TLS libraries will reject connections using expired certificates.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="common-causes"&gt;Common Causes&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-c" data-lang="c"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Cause 1: Server certificate expired
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Certificate not renewed before expiry
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Cause 2: System clock wrong
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Clock set to wrong date
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Cause 3: Certificate authority expired
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Intermediate CA certificate expired
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="how-to-fix"&gt;How to Fix&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3 id="fix-1-renew-the-certificate"&gt;Fix 1: Renew the certificate&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Let&amp;#39;s Encrypt&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;certbot renew
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Self-signed&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;openssl x509 -in old.pem -out new.pem -days &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;365&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id="fix-2-check-system-clock"&gt;Fix 2: Check system clock&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;date
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;timedatectl status
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id="fix-3-bypass-check-testing-only"&gt;Fix 3: Bypass check (testing only)&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-c" data-lang="c"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;SSL_CTX_set_verify&lt;/span&gt;(ctx, SSL_VERIFY_NONE, NULL); &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// NOT for production
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="examples"&gt;Examples&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Check certificate expiry&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;openssl s_client -connect example.com:443 &amp;lt;/dev/null 2&amp;gt;/dev/null | &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;\
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; openssl x509 -noout -dates
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Check local certificate&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;openssl x509 -in cert.pem -noout -dates
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="related-errors"&gt;Related Errors&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/c/tls-handshake-failure/"&gt;TLS handshake failure&lt;/a&gt; — general TLS error.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/c/certificate-revoked/"&gt;Certificate revoked&lt;/a&gt; — revoked certificate.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/c/hostname-mismatch/"&gt;Hostname mismatch&lt;/a&gt; — hostname error.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;</description></item><item><title>[Solution] crypto/x509 Certificate Error Fix</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/go/go-x509-error/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/go/go-x509-error/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="cryptox509-certificate-error"&gt;crypto/x509 Certificate Error&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Fix Go x509 certificate errors. Handle certificate validation, chain verification, and format issues..&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="what-this-error-means"&gt;What This Error Means&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Common error scenarios include:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Connection or network failures&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Invalid configuration or options&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Resource not found or unavailable&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Permission or access denied&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id="common-causes"&gt;Common Causes&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-go" data-lang="go"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Cause 1: Incorrect configuration or missing setup&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Cause 2: Network or connection issues&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Cause 3: Invalid input or parameters&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Cause 4: Missing dependencies or resources&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="how-to-fix"&gt;How to Fix&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3 id="fix-1-verify-configuration-and-setup"&gt;Fix 1: Verify configuration and setup&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-go" data-lang="go"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Check configuration values and ensure required setup&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Verify the service/library is properly configured&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id="fix-2-add-proper-error-handling"&gt;Fix 2: Add proper error handling&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-go" data-lang="go"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;result&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;err&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;:=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;doSomething&lt;/span&gt;()
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;err&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;!=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;nil&lt;/span&gt; {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;log&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;Printf&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;Error: %v&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;err&lt;/span&gt;)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;return&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;err&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;}
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id="fix-3-add-retry-and-timeout-logic"&gt;Fix 3: Add retry and timeout logic&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-go" data-lang="go"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;ctx&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;cancel&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;:=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;context&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;WithTimeout&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;context&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;Background&lt;/span&gt;(), &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;30&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;*&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;time&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;Second&lt;/span&gt;)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;defer&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;cancel&lt;/span&gt;()
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Use context for timeouts on operations&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;result&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;err&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;:=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;doWork&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;ctx&lt;/span&gt;)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;err&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;!=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;nil&lt;/span&gt; {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;ctx&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;Err&lt;/span&gt;() &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;==&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;context&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;DeadlineExceeded&lt;/span&gt; {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;log&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;Println&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;Operation timed out&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; }
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;}
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="examples"&gt;Examples&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-go" data-lang="go"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;package&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;main&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;import&lt;/span&gt; (
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;context&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;fmt&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;log&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;time&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;func&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;main&lt;/span&gt;() {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;ctx&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;cancel&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;:=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;context&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;WithTimeout&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;context&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;Background&lt;/span&gt;(), &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;5&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;*&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;time&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;Second&lt;/span&gt;)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;defer&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;cancel&lt;/span&gt;()
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;result&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;err&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;:=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;doWork&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;ctx&lt;/span&gt;)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;err&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;!=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;nil&lt;/span&gt; {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;log&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;Fatalf&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;Error: %v&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;err&lt;/span&gt;)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; }
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;fmt&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;Println&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;result&lt;/span&gt;)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;}
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="related-errors"&gt;Related Errors&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/go/context-deadline/"&gt;context-deadline&lt;/a&gt; — context deadline exceeded&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/go/net-dial/"&gt;net-dial&lt;/a&gt; — connection refused&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/go/io-eof/"&gt;io-eof&lt;/a&gt; — I/O error&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;</description></item><item><title>[Solution] Go TLS Handshake Failure / Certificate Verify Failed — Runtime Error Fix</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/go/tls-error/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/go/tls-error/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="tls-handshake-failure--certificate-verify-failed"&gt;TLS Handshake Failure / Certificate Verify Failed&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The error &lt;code&gt;tls: handshake failure&lt;/code&gt; or &lt;code&gt;x509: certificate signed by unknown authority&lt;/code&gt; occurs when a TLS/SSL connection cannot be established due to certificate validation failure, protocol mismatch, or missing certificate configuration.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="description"&gt;Description&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;TLS (Transport Layer Security) requires both client and server to present valid certificates and agree on cipher suites. Handshake failures happen when the certificate chain is invalid, the certificate has expired, the hostname does not match, or the client and server cannot agree on a protocol version.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>[Solution] Linux openssl Certificate Error — Fix</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/os/linux/linux-openssl-error/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/os/linux/linux-openssl-error/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="linux-openssl-certificate-error"&gt;Linux: openssl: certificate error&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The &lt;code&gt;openssl: certificate error&lt;/code&gt; message means the OpenSSL library encountered a problem verifying or processing an SSL/TLS certificate. This can occur when using &lt;code&gt;openssl s_client&lt;/code&gt;, &lt;code&gt;openssl verify&lt;/code&gt;, or when applications linked against OpenSSL fail certificate validation.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="what-this-error-means"&gt;What This Error Means&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;OpenSSL is the underlying cryptographic library used by most Linux tools for SSL/TLS. Certificate errors in OpenSSL indicate the certificate chain cannot be validated against the trusted CA store, the certificate is malformed, expired, or the hostname doesn&amp;rsquo;t match. Understanding the specific error code helps identify the root cause.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>